data.description: Welcome Home! This 4 bedroom, 2 full bathroom property located in the University area is perfect for First Time Home Buyers and/or Investors. The property has an open floor plan, with the primary bedroom being located on the main level. The laundry area is located on the 2nd floor, along with 3 guest bedrooms and bathroom. Centrally located along the path of progress, within the University area with very close proximity to the Light Rail Linx Blue Line. ASK ABOUT THE POSSIBLE SELLER CREDITS. Illustration is attached within the MLS. Schedule your private showing today!
